# Auto deploy (hy-webagent)

When finishing a task that changes this repo in a deployable way:

1. Commit (follow repo commit style).
2. `git push origin main`.
3. Run `./scripts/remote-update.sh` (uses `~/.config/hy-webagent/deploy.env`).
4. Confirm health / service status in the reply.

Do **not** ask “要不要部署” — deploy by default unless the user explicitly says not to, or the change is docs-only / local-scratch / clearly not for production.
